name: PHASEAssetError.Code
desc: Codes that identify framework asset errors.

items.name: case alreadyExists
items.desc: An error the asset registry throws when the app registers an asset twice by the same name.

items.name: case badParameters
items.desc: An error that indicates an asset registry call contains invalid data.

items.name: case failedToLoad
items.desc: An error that indicates an asset failed to load.

items.name: case generalError
items.desc: An error the asset registry throws when an unspecified problem occurs.

items.name: case invalidEngineInstance
items.desc: An error that indicates an asset registry call references an invalid engine.

items.name: case memoryAllocation
items.desc: An error the framework throws when an asset depletes system memory.
